Fem%3E%20of%20marriage.%20In%20Scandinavian%20culture%2C%20this%20is%20a%20very%20typical%20lifestyle%20choice.%20It's%20so%20usual%2C%20so%20mundane%2C%20there's%20a%20neat%20word%20just%20to%20describe%20it.%20Its%20definition%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20there's%20no%20need%20for%20superfluous%20explanation%20or%20justification%20of%20a%20decision%20to%20simply%20be%20together%20without%20the%20legality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20have%20been%20together%20for%20nearly%2010%20years%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-separately-from-long-term-partner-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20unconventionally%3C%2Fa%3E%20despite%20our%20monogamous%20commitment.%20We've%20overcome%20all%20of%20the%20usual%20hurdles%20of%20long-term%20relationships%20and%20have%20landed%20on%20a%20situation%20that%20works%20for%20us.%20I%20value%20that%20neither%20of%20us%20considers%20the%20paint-by-numbers%2C%20white-picket-fence-or-bust%20approach%20to%20love%20to%20define%20our%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291cd6c73-c7db-43ee-8385-17f050d5b269%5C%22%3EWe've%20never%20wanted%20to%20get%20married%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20antiquated%20origin%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2025-wedding-trends-in-and-out-from-planner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewedding%20industry%20is%20booming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20some%2C%20they%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20sense%20and%20are%20beautiful%20celebrations%20of%20love.%20While%20we%20never%20felt%20the%20urge%2C%20I%20do%20see%20the%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20knows%20what%20the%20terms%20%3Cem%3Ehusband%2C%20wife%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Espouse%20%3C%2Fem%3Emean.%20They%20denote%20a%20certain%20seriousness%2C%20beyond%20reproach.%20When%20you%20veer%20from%20the%20conventional%20vernacular%2C%20people%20tend%20to%20require%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20decision%20not%20to%20walk%20down%20the%20aisle%20doesn't%20denote%20a%20casualness%20about%20our%20partnership.%20It%20actually%20causes%20us%20to%20talk%20more%20about%20what%20love%20is%20without%20convention%2C%20and%20means%20we've%20had%20more%20conversations%20about%20what%20makes%20us%2C%20us.%20We've%20been%20able%20to%20forge%20our%20own%20path%20and%20build%20something%20unique%20to%20our%20circumstances%2C%20something%20that%20will%20stand%20well%20on%20its%20own%20without%20the%20foundations%20of%20societal%20norms.%20We%20choose%20each%20other%2C%20every%20day%2C%20not%20because%20of%20paperwork%20or%20the%20State%20of%20New%20York%20or%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20extended%20family%2C%20it%20becomes%20more%20complicated.%20My%20partner's%20mother%20is%20someone%20I%20introduce%20as%20my%20partner's%20mother%2C%20not%20my%20mother-in-law.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnever-wanted-kids-partner-son-relationship-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMy%20partner's%20son%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20his%20son%2C%20not%20my%20stepson%2C%20despite%20the%20love%20and%20length%20of%20our%20direct%20relationship.%20My%20sister%20is%20my%20sister%2C%20not%20his%20sister-in-law%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20mourn%20the%20directness%2C%20the%20cleanness%20of%20lines%20of%20those%20relationships.%20Sometimes%20I%20wonder%20if%20it%20would%20be%20easier%20to%20simply%20use%20the%20terms%20most%20familiar%2C%20the%20ones%20considered%20common%20denominators%20of%20definition%20that%20would%20link%20me%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-in-law-travel-bonding-closer-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20I%20now%20consider%20family%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20to%20what%20end%3F%20And%20at%20what%20cost%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarriage%20has%20never%20felt%20like%20a%20natural%20step%20for%20me%2C%20nor%20an%20honest%20desire.%20Instead%20of%20adding%20to%20my%20life%2C%20I%20always%20felt%20like%20I%20would%20lose%20something%20by%20taking%20that%20step%2C%20some%20part%20of%20my%20individuality%20that%20I've%20always%20wanted%20to%20maintain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7fb741b-fefc-4106-ab8c-fd38c9f488b4%5C%22%3ESometimes%2C%20it's%20easier%20to%20let%20people%20assume%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20there%20are%20moments%20when%20people%20assume%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20correct%20them.%20When%20we've%20been%20faced%20with%20health%20emergencies%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-partner-couple-travel-together-full-time-one-date-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhile%20we're%20traveling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sometimes%20I%20catch%20myself%20in%20an%20allowance%20that%20isn't%20quite%20a%20lie%20but%20is%20also%20not%20quite%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20went%20away%20for%20our%20annual%20autumn%20trip%20to%20the%20Hudson%20Valley.%20After%20checking%20into%20the%20hotel%2C%20I%20had%20a%20migraine%20but%20realized%20I%20forgot%20my%20pain%20medication.%20When%20he%20asked%20the%20front%20desk%20about%20a%20first%20aid%20kit%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20has%20a%20migraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noted%20this%20linguistic%20choice%20but%20didn't%20need%20to%20ask%20about%20it%3B%20I%20knew%20why%20he%20made%20that%20choice.%20%3Cem%3EWife%3C%2Fem%3E%20holds%20more%20weight%20than%20%3Cem%3Egirlfriend%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Those%20terms%2C%20that%20relationship%20%E2%80%94%20they%20carry%20an%20importance%2C%20a%20seriousness%20that's%20so%20understood%20it%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20qualified.%20I%20wish%20that%20our%20commitment%20held%20enough%20of%20that%20weight%2C%20by%20the%20sheer%20nature%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20ours%2C%20but%20I%20understand%20that%20we're%20not%20there%20yet%2C%20societally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20love%20without%20convention%3F%20Even%20if%20progressive%20society%20gives%20allowance%20for%20new%20rules%2C%20it%20hasn't%20caught%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fson-loves-explaining-slang-words-helps-us-connect-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20still%20matters%20more%20than%20I'd%20care%20to%20admit.%20I%20hope%20someday%20we%20all%20allow%20ourselves%20%E2%80%94%20and%20others%20%E2%80%94%20whatever%20definitions%20feel%20right%2C%20and%20that%20it's%20palatable%20and%20can%20be%20translated%20outwardly%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20proud%20that%20he%20is%20not%20my%20husband%2C%20and%20that%20I'm%20not%20a%20wife.%20I'm%20proud%20of%20whatever%20it%20is%20that%20we%20are%20because%20it's%20unique%2C%20specific%2C%20and%20just%20ours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20have%20a%20headache%20in%20the%20Hudson%20Valley%3F%20Sure%2C%20I'll%20let%20people%20think%20I'm%20a%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-married-partner-easier-let-people-assume-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753615621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68826f23f748d8c055f63872%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-married-partner-easier-let-people-assume-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20partner%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20married.%20However%2C%20the%20terms%20%26quot%3Bhusband%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwife%26quot%3B%20hold%20more%20weight%2C%20so%20sometimes%2C%20we%20let%20people%20assume.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alexandra%20Saville)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-married-partner-easier-let-people-assume-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Winnie%20Harlow%20stuns%20in%20sultry%20birthday%20pics%20as%20she%20celebrates%20turning%2031%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A175361533