%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarted-freelancing-penny-a-word-never-gave-up-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efreelance%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20felt%20my%20career%20was%20much%20more%20aligned%20with%20my%20purpose.%20I%20was%20living%20for%20a%20living%2C%20and%20no%20longer%20dreading%20going%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e11a2e9-77bf-4121-b46a-d5b56305bb6a%5C%22%3EI%20later%20learned%20about%20a%20family%20I%20didn't%20know%20existed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%2C%20however%2C%20that%20the%20biggest%20catalyst%20for%20change%20after%20Marguerite's%20death%20wasn't%20the%20money%20she%20left%20me%3A%20It%20was%20the%20realization%20of%20a%20family%20secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20went%20through%20her%20papers%2C%20I%20learned%20about%20my%20grandmother's%20stepdaughter%2C%20whom%20I%20never%20knew%20existed.%20I%20also%20learned%20that%20Marguerite%20had%20cousins%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-extended-family-pros-cons-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eextended%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20had%20never%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20that%20family%20helped%20me%20feel%20whole.%20I%20fostered%20relationships%20with%20them%20and%20deepened%20relationships%20with%20my%20friends.%20Marguerite's%20death%20was%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20she%20was%20in%20her%2080s%20when%20she%20died%2C%20her%20death%20reinforced%20to%20me%20that%20life%20is%20short.%20I%20want%20to%20spend%20my%20time%20with%20the%20people%20and%20projects%20that%20are%20most%20important%20to%20me.%20Thanks%20to%20my%20grandmother%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrandmother-left-large-inheritance-took-years-off-work-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753612622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.co