tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-style-break-generational-curses-raise-child-parents-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewanted%20to%20parent%20differently%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2030%2C%20I%20had%20a%20son.%20Over%20the%20next%20eight%20years%2C%20I%20had%20three%20more%20kids.%20Rather%20than%20pull%20scary%20tales%20from%20the%20daily%20news%20or%20the%20town%20rumor%20mill%2C%20I%20kept%20them%20sheltered.%20When%20they%20asked%20about%20issues%20I%20thought%20could%20be%20frightening%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20explain%20in%20a%20way%20that%20was%20both%20direct%20and%20sensitive.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-mental-health-experts-wish-you-knew-about-anxiety%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverwhelming%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20struggled%20with%20made%20it%20difficult%2C%20though%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20knew%20it%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe373737-30be-4cdd-92d9-66a7678e06d2%5C%22%3EI%20learned%20that%20my%20son%20dealt%20with%20similar%20anxieties%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERetrospection%20can%20be%20difficult%20as%20a%20parent.%20It%20often%20provides%20an%20overarching%2C%20distanced%20perspective%20we%20don't%20have%20when%20our%20children%20are%20little.%20Maybe%20this%20was%20why%20I%20was%20caught%20off%20guard%20when%20my%2020-year-old%20son%20came%20over%20to%20have%20dinner%20one%20night%20and%20announced%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20afraid%20of%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20what%20%26quot%3Beverything%26quot%3B%20included%2C%20he%20delivered%20a%20list%20as%20long%20as%20my%20own.%20It%20included%20driving%2C%20fire%2C%20water%2C%20and%20a%20million%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20passed%20all%20the%20fear%20from%20when%20you%20grew%20up%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Though%20I%20had%20aimed%20to%20raise%20my%20children%20differently%20from%20how%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b