ey%20rely%20too%20much%20on%20AI%2C%20there%20can%20be%20a%20tangible%20boost%20for%20more%20reserved%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Smith%20is%20an%20organizational%20psychologist%20who%20runs%20a%20leadership%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iabusinessadvisors.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvisory%20firm%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He's%20seen%20AI%20supercharge%20the%20abilities%20of%20some%20of%20the%20quieter%20people%20on%20his%20team%2C%20who%20he%20said%20sometimes%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20engage%20with%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20team%20members%20have%20been%20able%20to%20query%20AI%20models%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20feedback%20they're%20getting%20from%20clients.%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20enabled%20introverted%20team%20members%20to%20become%20more%20confident%20and%20%26quot%3Bstart%20to%20have%20better%20human%20conversations%20with%20the%20people%20that%20they%20were%20originally%20having%20difficulty%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20for%20all%20the%20help%20AI%20can%20give%20workers%20of%20all%20personality%20types%2C%20it%20can't%20do%20everything%2C%20said%20Schneider%2C%20from%20fileAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20a%20bot%20won't%20be%20a%20big%20help%2C%20he%20said%2C%20if%20he%20has%20to%20talk%20to%20an%20investor%20in%20person.%20He%20still%20needs%20those%20interpersonal%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20upskill%20me%2C%20and%20it%20can%20sort%20of%20give%20me%20the%20playbook%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20standing%20there%2C%20and%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20to%20deliver%2C%26quot%3B%20Schneider%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonality-hire-introvert-extrovert-ai-work-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753608421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883b8003d5881a