blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenius-act-passed-two-retailers-are-considering-stablecoins-wmt-amzn-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20and%20Walmart%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20considering%20issuing%20stablecoins.%20Market%20experts%20say%20such%20a%20move%20could%20allow%20companies%20to%20bypass%20credit%20card%20transaction%20fees%20by%20having%20customers%20use%20their%20native%20stablecoins.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Cuy%20Sheffield%2C%20the%20head%20of%20crypto%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fv-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVisa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20payments%20giant%20sees%20the%20rise%20of%20stablecoins%20as%20an%20opportunity.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheffield%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Visa%20isn't%20worried%20about%20corporations%20adopting%20stablecoins%2C%20even%20if%20they%20offer%20consumers%20a%20new%20way%20to%20make%20payments%20that%20doesn't%20involve%20credit%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f99e1440-2e00-4a2b-9e79-150d5bccf19a%5C%22%3EOpportunity%20in%20a%20new%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESheffield%20said%20that%20he%20doesn't%20think%20stablecoins%20will%20dramatically%20impact%20how%20most%20consumers%20shop%20in%20the%20US.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20really%20think%20stablecoins%20solve%20much%20of%20a%20problem%20for%20retail%20payments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20thinks%20the%20US%20payments%20infrastructure%20already%20works%20well%20for%20US%20consumers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Visa's%20data%20shows%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20stablecoin%20volume%20is%20generated%20by%20%26quot%3Bhigh-value%20transfers%2C%20not%20retail%20transactions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheffield%20said%20that%20Visa%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisa-crypto-exec-details-opportunity-stable-coins-b2b-payments-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehas%20seen%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20potential%20of%20stablecoins%20to%20transform%20global%20payments%20for%20years.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3BWe%20support%20many%20different%20currencies%20on%20our%20network%20today.%20A%20stable%20coin%20isn't%20even%20a%20new%20currency%2C%20really.%20It's%20just%20another%20way%20to%20represent%20an%20existing%20currency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20later%2C%20the%20company%20sees%20even%20more%20opportunity%20in%20the%20stablecoin%20market%2C%20as%20new%20policies%20help%20spur%20mainstream%20adoption.%20Sheffield%20said%20that%20Visa%20sees%20the%20opportunity%20mainly%20outside%20the%20US%2C%20specifically%20in%20emerging%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20the%20opportunity%20for%20stable%20coins%20is%20overwhelmingly%20outside%20the%20United%20States%2C%20emerging%20market%20focused%20economies%20where%20there's%20demand%20for%20dollars%20and%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20access%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheffield%20said%20that%20stablecoins%20may%20be%20enticing%20for%20people%20who%20need%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20cross-border%20payments%2C%20which%20can%20be%20slow.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20sees%20Visa%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20emerging%20markets%20in%20helping%20consumers%20become%20comfortable%20holding%20and%20using%20stablecoins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20activity%20in%20Latin%20America%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Colombia%2C%20Chile%2C%20Argentina%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Visa%20had%20also%20seen%20high%20activity%20in%20Kenya%2C%20Nigeria%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20that%20the%20most%20impact%20we'll%20have%20will%20be%20democratizing%20many%20emerging%20systems%20and%20providing%20dollars%20for%20places%20that%20weren't%20really%20prepared%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Sheffield's%20view%2C%20stablecoins%20could%20be%20the%20bridge%20that%20helps%20connect%20emerging%20markets%20with%20companies%20in%20developed%20economies%2C%20ultimately%20creating%20economic%20opportunity%20in%20both%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20serve%20consumers%20and%20markets%20that%20haven't%20really%20had%20many%20things%20that%20we've%20had%20in%20the%20US%20and%20in%20Europe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3B%20I%20think%20stablecoins%20will%20become%20this%20platform%20that%20many%20different%20companies%20will%20build%20on%20top%20of%20to%20offer%20modern%2C%20efficient%20products%20in%20emerging%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstablecoins-crypto-visa-emerging-markets-wmt-amzn-retail-consumers-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753606801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883d0e33d5881a51c1e0965%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstablecoins-crypto-visa-emerging-markets-wmt-amzn-retail-consumers-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20stablecoin%20momentum%20surges%2C%20Visa's%20head%20of%20crypto%20says%20he%20isn't%20worried%20about%20disruptions%20to%20traditional%20payments%20systems.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A67%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstablecoins-crypto-visa-emerging-markets-wmt-amzn-retail-consumers-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDeclare%20Meat%2C%20Fruits%2C%20Soil%26quot%3B%3A%20US'%20Warning%20To%20People%20Travelling%20With%20Food%20At%20Airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20post%20on%20X%20showed%20a%20detection%20dog%20inspecting%20a%20cooked%20pig's%20head%20wrapped%20in%20foil%2C%20along%20with%20bottles%20of%20what%20