%20human-wildlife%20conflicts%20were%20valid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202020%20report%20spotlights%20how%2C%20in%20areas%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20sloth%20bears%20are%20still%20victims%20of%20poaching.%20The%20reason%20lies%20in%20retaliatory%20killings%20when%20the%20bears%20come%20in%20contact%20with%20human%20settlements.%20A%202014%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EWorld%20Wildlife%20Fund%20%3C%2Fem%3Espotlighted%20how%20farmers%20in%20the%20Kanha-Pench%20Corridor%20estimate%20that%20they%20annually%20lose%2030-50%20percent%20of%20their%20crop%20due%20to%20crop%20raiding%20by%20wild%20ungulates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%202023%20report%2C%20which%20spoke%20about%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20being%20home%20to%20the%20highest%20tiger%20population%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20the%20state%20has%20nine%20tiger%20reserves%20%E2%80%94%20underscored%20this%20as%20also%20the%20reason%20for%20human-tiger%20tussles.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20forest%20area%20in%20MP%20reportedly%20shrank%20by%203%20percent%20as%20noted%20in%202017%2C%20and%20it%20is%20considered%20a%20major%20reason%20for%20human-wildlife%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20stated.%20A%20decrease%20in%20forest%20cover%20and%20human%20encroachment%20compounds%20the%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20reports%20shine%20a%20light%20on%20why%20the%20area%20around%20Jamtara%20is%20key%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F462584%2Fladakh-snow-leopard-conservation-community-living-with-snow-leopards-survey-insights-population-study%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocusing%20on%20wildlife%20preservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Coming%20from%20a%20line%20of%20conservationists%2C%20Amit%20says%20the%20endeavour%20has%20always%20been%20to%20facilitate%20change%20on%20the%20ground.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20Tiger%20Trust%20is%20an%20NGO%20our%20family%20started%2C%20we%20also%20do%20individual%20programmes%20to%20support%20and%20train%20guides%